0:06:40.864,000 --> 0:06:41,000
What are you doing?

139
0:06:42.156,000 --> 0:06:43,000
(Applause)

140
0:06:43.331,000 --> 0:06:45,000
And as for you, everybody here in this room,

141
0:06:45.443,000 --> 0:06:46,000
I leave you with two marching orders.

142
0:06:47.284,000 --> 0:06:48,000
Get in the game,

143
0:06:48.483,000 --> 0:06:5,000
and the way you get in it is educate yourself,

144
0:06:50.696,000 --> 0:06:51,000
build awareness around yourself,

145
0:06:52.261,000 --> 0:06:54,000
and then also advocate for e-government solutions.

146
