0:07:24.927,000 --> 0:07:25,000
instead of the 45 percent,

159
0:07:26.236,000 --> 0:07:28,000
do you really think that I would have to go a pay a bribe?

160
0:07:28.998,000 --> 0:07:29,000
That's what breeds corruption.

161
0:07:30.8,000 --> 0:07:34,000
Bad laws, sets of horrible, nonsense laws.

162
0:07:35.276,000 --> 0:07:37,000
(Applause) (Cheers)

163
0:07:37.688,000 --> 0:07:38,000
Right?

164
0:07:38.863,000 --> 0:07:43,000
(Applause)

165
0:07:44.196,000 --> 0:07:45,000
You want to fight corruption?

166
0:07:46.03,000 --> 0:07:47,000
That's what you do.

167
0:07:47.26,000 --> 0:07:49,000
And again, remember, you don't need to wait for anyone.

168
0:07:49.861,000 --> 0:07:5,000
You can do that by yourself.

169
0:07:51.259,000 --> 0:07:53,000
