178
0:08:17.879,000 --> 0:08:18,000
They're going to go for violence.

179
0:08:19.506,000 --> 0:08:2,000
And none of us wants that.

180
0:08:21.094,000 --> 0:08:22,000
None, none of us.

181
0:08:22.807,000 --> 0:08:23,000
That's the one way it can go.

182
0:08:24.244,000 --> 0:08:25,000
