0:08:44.929,000 --> 0:08:45,000
It can happen in two ways --

190
0:08:46.347,000 --> 0:08:49,000
pick violence or you pick the calm, productive way.

191
0:08:49.522,000 --> 0:08:5,000
I want the calm, productive way.

192
0:08:51.101,000 --> 0:08:53,000
None of us should ever, ever even try to think

193
0:08:53.379,000 --> 0:08:55,000
about what else could happen if we don't go there.

194
0:08:55.77,000 --> 0:08:56,000
So, please.

195
